{"tid":2103663,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"美議員警告承認台獨合法性     懲罰北京","createTime":"2020-07-11T11:10:19.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-13T18:12:42.000Z","uid":79563,"like":347,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":73,"replies":[{"pid":"a57e0617cf4c9a89a0de84423654e671feafdb95","tid":2103663,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:10:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/u_fOmdk2KCYCgaHVV9Rf9A--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/https://media-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com/creatr-uploaded-images/2020-07/7658b100-c352-11ea-95fe-3195b5f23e81\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fu_fOmdk2KCYCgaHVV9Rf9A--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fmedia-mbst-pub-ue1.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fcreatr-uploaded-images%2F2020-07%2F7658b100-c352-11ea-95fe-3195b5f23e81&h=9a31ac1b&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n《港區國安法》實施引起美國大力反對，美國眾議院外交關係委員會共和黨首席議員麥考爾（Michael McCaul）近日受訪時指摘，北京正推動接管香港，非常希望控制9月的立法會選舉，決定港人未來的命運，意味香港將不再自治。他稱不會讓台灣發生同類情況，揚言對大陸「最嚴厲的懲罰措施就是承認台灣作為一個獨立國家的合法性」。<br />\n<br />\n麥考爾在訪問中提到《港區國安法》的實施，是剝奪香港人的自由和民主。他指香港現在幾乎是個警察國家，北京當局打着國安法的帽子，實際上是要接管香港，違反「一國兩制」的條約。因此美國共和黨和民主黨在國會通過《香港自治法》，對北京當局釋放強烈信號，以示他們認真關注香港事態發展。<br />\n<br />\n對於眾議院中國工作小組中只剩下共和黨成員，麥考爾感到遺憾，認為民主黨出於政治原因而撤出，眼見現在的中國共產黨，應好好審視他們的外交政策。他與許多美國駐外大使交談後，認為歐洲盟友亦開始意識到中國問題敲響了警鐘，希望看到更多相關政策出台。<br />\n<br />\n有指《港區國安法》可能是中國大陸處理台灣問題的藍圖，被問及美國應就兩岸安全議題採取甚麼行動時，麥考爾表示同意美國對台灣出售F16戰機，以協助台灣自衞。他指大陸的長遠計劃是奪回台灣，但美國不會允許這種事情發生。他又稱，「承認台灣作為一個獨立國家的合法性」，將是非常重大的外交政策決定。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/港區國安法美議員警告承認台獨合法性-懲罰北京-084302115.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F%E6%B8%AF%E5%8D%80%E5%9C%8B%E5%AE%89%E6%B3%95%E7%BE%8E%E8%AD%B0%E5%93%A1%E8%AD%A6%E5%91%8A%E6%89%BF%E8%AA%8D%E5%8F%B0%E7%8D%A8%E5%90%88%E6%B3%95%E6%80%A7-%E6%87%B2%E7%BD%B0%E5%8C%97%E4%BA%AC-084302115.html&d=FEUhZFrEoh9TukhHyG%2BZyPUUj30esm9w7dCaRgXMgeE%3D&h=81692ef1\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/港區國安法美議員警告承認台獨合法性-懲罰北京-084302115.html</a>"},{"pid":"41724ba29e4d9936c829c112e81c4d1842c4fdd8","tid":2103663,"uid":25858,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:11:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"62c92bd6491ae16a55afb2dccc5acd8eb09964f5","tid":2103663,"uid":231583,"like":117,"dislike":1,"score":116,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:11:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"647c8dc5f09eb72680aea24a6470379083596cd3","tid":2103663,"uid":46245,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:12:42.000Z","msg":"不如直接啲，同中共斷交，再同中華民國建交吧"},{"pid":"e0adb068fcffcdeeb0a99a2b1d4b16c84df439a2","tid":2103663,"uid":117689,"like":55,"dislike":2,"score":53,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:13:53.000Z","msg":"承認香港係獨立國家仲爆<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6ebfa26167d093795a51cbb4f1c2eb57488fd64","tid":2103663,"uid":8948,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"62c92bd6491ae16a55afb2dccc5acd8eb09964f5","tid":2103663,"uid":231583,"like":117,"dislike":1,"score":116,"citedBy":5,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:11:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 諗起台灣研發個部戰機型到想打J<br />\n再買埋F16 應該又再進化<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/jable.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3d77433350ab87d56e0200ecbae2d9dd994f97","tid":2103663,"uid":205469,"like":42,"dislike":0,"score":42,"quote":{"pid":"647c8dc5f09eb72680aea24a6470379083596cd3","tid":2103663,"uid":46245,"like":86,"dislike":0,"score":86,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2020-07-11T11:12:42.00